  "text": "Cells were seeded in six-well plates (5 × 10 4 ) and, after 24 h, treated with 0.0 or 1.0 M of 2ME. After fixation, SA-␤gal cytochemical detection was performed according to Debacq-Chainiaux and collaborators [CITATION_1] . Plates were further incubated overnight at 37 • C. Blue stained cells were detected under a bright-field microscope for senescence evaluation.",
